GENERATIVE AI

SUMMARY
The assessment confirms that generative AI usage in processing Amex data is addressed, and that controls to restrict or disable such usage are in place, based on satisfactory statements from stakeholders. However, no supporting evidence was provided to validate these assertions.

KEY POINTS

Generative AI usage with Amex data is addressed in the assessment.

Controls to restrict or disable generative AI usage are reported as present.

Assessor is satisfied with stakeholder statements.

No evidence was shown to support these controls.

Section score is unavailable.


CONCLUSION
While verbal assurance has been given regarding controls over generative AI and Amex data, the lack of evidence introduces a risk that the controls may not be fully documented or implemented.
